The Lakers defeated the Warriors, 120-112 tonight in Los Angeles. LeBron James finished with a season-high 42 points along with 17 rebounds and 8 assists for the Lakers, while Austin Reaves tallied 23 points, 4 assists and 3 rebounds in the game.
